<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verify Your Access - ReceiptIQ</title>
    <style>
        body, table, td, a { -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; }
        body { margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; background-color: #0b0f19; }
        
        .email-canvas {
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #0b0f19;
            background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, #1a2238 0%, #0b0f19 80%);
            padding: 60px 20px;
        }

        .premium-card {
            max-width: 540px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 24px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
        }

        .card-header {
            padding: 40px 40px 20px 40px;
        }

        .brand-name {
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: #0b0f19;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #ede9fe;
            color: #7c3aed;
            padding: 6px 14px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.2px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        .card-body {
            padding: 0 40px 30px 40px;
        }

        .greeting-text {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #334155;
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .highlight-name {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #0b0f19;
        }

        .otp-display-unit {
            background-color: #0b0f19;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 35px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .otp-eyebrow {
            color: #94a3b8;
            font-size: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            display: block;
        }

        .otp-code {
            font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #a78bfa;
            letter-spacing: 16px;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .meta-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .meta-table td {
            padding: 16px 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .meta-label {
            color: #64748b;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .meta-value {
            color: #0b0f19;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: right;
        }

        .status-dot {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            background-color: #22c55e;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-right: 6px;
        }

        .security-banner {
            background-color: #fff1f2;
            border-left: 4px solid #e11d48;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #9f1239;
        }

        .email-footer {
            max-width: 540px;
            margin: 30px auto 0;
            text-align: center;
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 12px;
        }

        .email-footer a {
            color: #94a3b8;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-canvas">
        
        <div class="premium-card">
            
            <div class="card-header">
                <div>
                    <h1 class="brand-name">ReceiptIQ</h1>
                    <div class="badge">Account Verification</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="greeting-text">
                    Hey <span class="highlight-name"><%= name %></span>,<br><br>
                    You're almost ready to start tracking your expenses, setting goals, and managing your financial baseline on <strong>ReceiptIQ</strong>.  
                    Use the verification code below to continue.
                </div>

                <div class="otp-display-unit">
                    <span class="otp-eyebrow">Your Verification Code</span>
                    <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
                </div>

                <table class="meta-table">
                    <tr>
                        <td class="meta-label">Code Expiry</td>
                        <td class="meta-value">2 Minutes</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="meta-label">Session Status</td>
                        <td class="meta-value"><span class="status-dot"></span> Secure</td>
                    </tr>
                </table>

                <div class="security-banner">
                    <strong>Keep this code private.</strong> ReceiptIQ will never ask for your verification code. If you didn’t request this, you can safely ignore this email.
                </div>
            </div>
            
        </div>

        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> ReceiptIQ. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>Didn’t request this? <a href="#">Review your account activity</a>.</p>
        </div>

    </div>
</body>
</html>
